content.rendered:
Directed by Sanjiv Jaiswal.

Written by Sanjiv Jaiswal.

Cast Rajeev Khandelwal(Ajay Singh). Atul Kulkarni(Inspector Rajpal Singh). Abhimanyu Singh(Gyanu Singh). Samiksha Oswal(Manjri (as Sameksha)). Vikram Gokhale(Tej Pratap Singh). Aniruddh Dave(Arjun (as Anirudh Dave)). Apoorva Arora(Soha). S.M. Zaheer(Deenanath) . Vikram Bhui(Siddhu). Shaji Chaudhary(thakur Bhanu pratap). Rajiv Dinkar(Raja). Tauqeer Alam Khan(Bhanu pratap Singh).Mukteshwara Ojha. Gauri Shankar(Professor singh (voice) (as Gauri shankar)). Prem Trivedi(Registrar of university). Uday Vir Singh Yadav(Judge)

Language Hindi.

Producers Sanjay Bali. Ramesh Chand. Nitin Mishra. Rajnish Ram Puri. Anil Singh. Sunil Singh.

Production Rudraksh Adventures.
